      "content": "the \"getting help\" thing just feels like another loop. go to therapist, feel slightly better for a month, crash, repeat. it's just more noise. i'm not looking for a lifeline or a crisis line, i'm just staring at the reality that this loop is inescapable. if the code is fundamentally broken, isn't the most logical thing to just stop running it?",
